data.description: Welcome to Pochard! This lovely two story home offers an open concept kitchen, living room and dining area! Off the back of the home is access to the backyard! The main level laundry room adds room for storage in addition to the double door pantry closet and utility closet! Upstairs is the large primary bedroom with its own bathroom and walk-in closet! There three additional bedrooms upstairs with a hallway full bath! The home being newer, with amazing natural light, recessed lighting, carpet and attached garage with additional driveway parking all in one is lovely and ready for you!
